      <title>GTD：一种高效的生活方式</title>
      <link>https://neuropix.github.io/posts/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/%E6%95%88%E7%8E%87/gtd%E4%B8%80%E7%A7%8D%E9%AB%98%E6%95%88%E7%9A%84%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F/</link>
